statements: SELECT user_id, behavior_type, behavior_description, last_interaction FROM UserBehavior;
SELECT behavior_type, behavior_description, user_id, last_interaction FROM UserBehavior WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM UserBehavior WHERE behavior_type = 'click' ORDER BY last_interaction ASC;
SELECT behavior_description, user_id FROM UserBehavior WHERE last_interaction > '2022-01-01' AND behavior_type = 'scroll' ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT user_id, behavior_type FROM UserBehavior WHERE behavior_description LIKE '%tutorial%' LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM UserBehavior WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, behavior_type, behavior_description FROM UserBehavior ORDER BY last_interaction DESC;
SELECT user_id, behavior_type, COUNT(*) AS behavior_count FROM UserBehavior GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT user_id, behavior_description FROM UserBehavior WHERE behavior_type = 'click' ORDER BY last_interaction ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT DISTINCT behavior_type FROM UserBehavior ORDER BY behavior_type;
SELECT * FROM user_profiles;
SELECT username, email FROM user_profiles;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM user_profiles WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT log_id, action_taken, timestamp FROM augmented_reality_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, action_taken FROM augmented_reality_logs WHERE action_taken LIKE '%click%';
SELECT * FROM user_profiles WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT user_id, email FROM user_profiles WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM augmented_reality_logs WHERE action_taken = 'login' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, action_taken FROM augmented_reality_logs WHERE timestamp >= '2023-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2023-01-31' ORDER BY action_taken ASC;
SELECT user_id, action_taken, timestamp FROM augmented_reality_logs WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001' AND action_taken LIKE '%camera%' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM users
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE user_id = 1
SELECT user_id, avatar_url FROM users ORDER BY user_id DESC
SELECT * FROM user_behaviors WHERE behavior_type = 'Likes' ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT * FROM ar_experiences WHERE user_id = 2 AND timestamp > '2022-01-01'
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT users.username, ar_experiences.ar_content_url FROM users JOIN ar_experiences ON users.user_id = ar_experiences.user_id WHERE users.user_id = 2;
SELECT user_id, MAX(timestamp) AS last_interaction FROM user_behaviors GROUP BY user_id;

SELECT users.username, user_behaviors.behavior_type, ar_experiences.timestamp FROM users LEFT JOIN user_behaviors ON users.user_id = user_behaviors.user_id LEFT JOIN ar_experiences ON users.user_id = ar_experiences.user_id;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT id, username, email FROM users ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT username, age FROM users WHERE age > 30;
SELECT id, behavior, timestamp FROM user_behavior WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM ar_experiences WHERE experience_name LIKE '%game%' ORDER BY experience_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM users WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY username DESC;
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT users.username, ar_experiences.experience_name FROM users INNER JOIN ar_experiences ON users.id = ar_experiences.user_id WHERE ar_experiences.behavior_trigger = 'click';
SELECT u.username, u.email, COUNT(a.id) AS num_experiences FROM users u LEFT JOIN ar_experiences a ON u.id = a.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING num_experiences > 2;

SELECT u.username, u.age, ae.experience_name, ab.timestamp FROM users u INNER JOIN ar_experiences ae ON u.id = ae.user_id INNER JOIN user_behavior ab ON u.id = ab.user_id WHERE u.age < 40 ORDER BY ab.timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE age > 18;
SELECT DISTINCT gender FROM users;
SELECT content_name, content_rating FROM ar_content ORDER BY content_rating DESC;
SELECT user_id, behavior_type, behavior_timestamp FROM user_behaviors WHERE behavior_timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM users ORDER BY age DESC, username ASC LIMIT 10

SELECT u.username, u.email, c.content_name FROM users u JOIN user_preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id JOIN ar_content c ON p.content_id = c.content_id WHERE p.preference_level BETWEEN 1 AND 3 ORDER BY c.content_rating DESC

SELECT u.username, u.age, COUNT(b.behavior_id) AS behavior_count FROM users u LEFT JOIN user_behaviors b ON u.user_id = b.user_id GROUP BY u.username, u.age HAVING behavior_count > 5 ORDER BY behavior_count DESC

SELECT u.username, u.email, d.device_name, c.content_name FROM users u JOIN ar_devices d ON u.user_id = d.user_id JOIN user_preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id JOIN ar_content c ON p.content_id = c.content_id WHERE u.gender = 'Male' AND d.device_type = 'AR Glasses'
SELECT u.username, NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM user_behaviors b WHERE b.user_id = u.user_id) AS has_no_behaviors FROM users u ORDER BY has_no_behaviors DESC, u.username ASC LIMIT 5
